				\begin{document}$$-0.16{\sigma }_{\mathrm{TWS}}/{\sigma }_{{G}_{{\rm{P}}}}$$\end{document}-0.16σTWS/σGP, compared with \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
