				\begin{document}$$\bar{P}$$\end{document}P¯). The three panels vary in sample size because of differing time availability of the precipitation datasets (Supplementary Table 2).

This identification strategy isolates the emergent interannual influence of precipitation concentration on TWS. The models are of the form2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
