The change in soil moisture stock is precipitation less soil evaporation, infiltration and saturation-excess ponding rate of water, and soil drainage. We simulate it as9\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
